{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"37445-khuku-o-boyal-mach","title":"খুকু ও বোয়াল মাছ","description":"বোয়াল মাছ খুকুর কাছে বড় এক নৌকা নিয়ে এলো। তারা দুজন মিলে পানির মধ্যেকার জগত দেখতে চায়। তারা যখন পানির ভেতর মাছেদের বাড়িঘর দেখছে, ঠিক তখনই একটি কুমির তাদের তাড়া করল। খুকু খুব ভয় পেল। বোয়াল মাছ কি পারবে খুকুকে কুমিরের হাত থেকে বাঁচাতে?","language":"Bengali","langCode":"bn","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Helal Arifeen"],"illustrators":["Mamun Hossain"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Room to Read","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/37445-khuku-o-boyal-mach"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93515/size3/de9c960accd220267c73aa15f0dd1401.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93515/size6/de9c960accd220267c73aa15f0dd1401.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/71882/size6/099d83a445e22738983338e7d1659ed7.jpg","text":"বিলের জলে নৌকা ভাসে,\nতাইনা দেখে খুকু হাসে।","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/71883/size6/c55bc1957f514cb5ec7429831467227a.jpg","text":"খুকুর সাথে শাপলা হাসে,\nমুখ উঁচিয়ে বোয়াল আসে।","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/71884/size6/2273914b872c808a9ea2ff557143387a.jpg","text":"আসবে নাকি আমার পিছু?\nবোয়াল বলে, বলবে কিছু!","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/71885/size6/013290e8a47182dba863676df7d47304.jpg","text":"খুকু বলে, পানসি নায়,\nচাইগো যেতে তোমার গাঁয়!","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/71886/size6/409c8026f75a01d973df2917408ace58.jpg","text":"শক্র দাঁতে দড়ি টানি,\nআনল বোয়াল নৌকাখানি।","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/71887/size6/61fba3a9c940d41e59f087e237e70edc.jpg","text":"নায়ে খুকু এলোকেশে, \nঅচিনপুরে যায় যে ভেসে।","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/71888/size6/1a2b4ee2f89589c9ad0c743d4eb17df0.jpg","text":"শেওলা যেন মাছের ঘর,","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/71889/size6/cf6d9a130b0b3fa2abf7502f597c0738.jpg","text":"খলসে পুঁটি তুলছে ঝড়।","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/71890/size6/72b82cd38ef152c5183bd073d8884a66.jpg","text":"ঢেউয়ের তালে নৌকা দোলে,\nহঠাৎ কুমির মাথা তোলে!","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/71891/size6/3e5b9ec6a25e5919d9c4ec5cf553bce0.jpg","text":"কাঁপছে খুকু থরথর, \nবোয়াল বলে, কিসের ডর?","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/71892/size6/8fde205e08f288c357066715e7c92e68.jpg","text":"নৌকা টানে, সাঁতার কাটে, \nফেরে বোয়াল বাড়ির ঘাটে।","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/71893/size6/b1bd377d965cf70edd0934af1d1356a2.jpg","text":"আসছে কুমির ধেয়ে ঐ, \nডাঙায় খুকু, বোয়াল কই?","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":12,"words":85}}